    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in mint, showroom-quality condition and represents the pinnacle of its model class. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and there are absolutely no dents, scratches, or imperfections to be found. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition, still carrying that new-car feel with zero wear on the upholstery or controls. Mechanically, the car is perfect; it has been meticulously maintained with a full service history, and every component functions exactly as it did the day it left the factory. For a buyer seeking a vehicle that is indistinguishable from new, this is an exceptional opportunity to own a truly well-preserved example.",
