      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to drive home a fantastic vehicle that\u2019s been well-loved and is in great shape! This car is in good condition, offering a reliable performance and a clean interior that makes every commute a pleasure. It has been well-maintained and is ready for its next adventure with you behind the wheel!",
