      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it's been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, so it's totally ready for its next adventure with you! Everything runs smoothly, and it\u2019s been super reliable for both daily commutes and fun weekend getaways. I've taken great care of it, and I'd love to see it go to a happy new home. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions\u2014I'm super happy to chat and tell you more about it!",
      "price": 31500.0,
