    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2018 Lexus RX 350, finished in a sophisticated Nebula Gray Pearl. This vehicle has been a reliable companion and is in solid condition throughout. The exterior retains a high-gloss finish, though there are minor stone chips on the leading edge of the hood and a small, superficial scuff on the rear bumper from city parking. Inside, the Parchment leather interior is clean and smoke-free; the bolsters show very light natural creasing but no cracks or tears. All premium amenities\u2014including the panoramic sunroof, heated and ventilated front seats, and the intuitive navigation system\u2014are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is excellent. It features a complete service history from Lexus-authorized centers, with the most recent oil change and multi-point inspection completed last month. The V6 engine runs whisper-quiet, and the transmission shifts seamlessly. The tires are matching Michelins with plenty of life left. This is a dependable, luxury SUV that looks great and drives even better, ready for its next owner with no immediate maintenance required.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
